videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets the ball in the post and shoots a jumper in rhythm for the bucket.
videos.headline: Ayton sinks smooth jumper

videos.description: Deandre Ayton tips in a high pass from Emmanuel Akot, becoming the leading freshman scorer in Arizona history.
videos.headline: Ayton leading freshman scorer in Arizona history

videos.description: Deandre Ayton has the ball with the shot clock winding down and drains a triple from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Ayton drills off-balanced 3

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright gets the ball and heaves a pass down the court to Deandre Ayton who finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Half-court pass sets up Ayton slam

videos.description: With the clock winding down, Justice Sueing fires a pass to Don Coleman who drains the 3 at the buzzer. The Golden Bears trail the Wildcats 38-35 at half.
videos.headline: Cal keeps it close with half-court heave

videos.description: Justice Sueing gets the ball in the lane and goes up-and-under through contact for the bucket.
videos.headline: Sueing's insane up-and-under layup falls for Cal

videos.description: Allonzo Trier drives and throws a beautiful bounce pass to Deandre Ayton for the dunk.
videos.headline: Trier dishes to Ayton for jam

videos.description: Allonzo Trier extends the Wildcats' lead with a steal and flashy finish.
videos.headline: Trier makes clutch steal and finish

videos.description: Sean Miller spoke about Arizona's resiliency over the past week in dealing with the controversy surrounding the program.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Miller looks at bigger picture after beating Cal) 2018/03/03

videos.headline: Miller looks at bigger picture after beating Cal
